    ],
    "text": "Homicide Reported \u2013 Neluwa Police Division",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      73.33,
      516.39,
      128.01
    ],
    "text": "Officers of the Neluwa Police Station have commenced investigations following a report received on the morning of 21 February 2026 regarding the fatal assault of a man with a sharp weapon and the injury of a woman in the Yaddehikandawatta area, within the Neluwa Police Division.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      142.45,
      501.34,
      155.73
    ],
    "text": "The deceased has been identified as a 67-year-old resident of the Morawaka area.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      170.29,
      504.51,
      211.17
    ],
    "text": "Preliminary investigations have revealed that the victim was attacked with a sharp instrument and killed over a land dispute. The injured woman is the wife of the deceased.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      225.73,
      524.59,
      266.64
    ],
    "text": "The body has been placed at the morgue of the Morawaka Hospital for a post-mortem examination. A 49-year-old suspect in connection with the murder has been taken into custody.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      281.08,
      399.55,
      294.36
    ],
    "text": "Further inquiries are being conducted by the Neluwa Police.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
